    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "idk. i was just looking at the stars and thinking about how much space there is. it's all just empty. everything we do, every single thing we feel or struggle for... it doesn't actually mean anything in the grand scheme of it all. it just feels like a lot of pointless noise before everything eventually just goes cold and dark. why even bother?",
